    "headline": "Verizon to report earnings July 24, 2026",
    "summary": "NEW YORK, June 26, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Verizon Communications Inc. (NYSE, Nasdaq: VZ) will report second-quarter 2026 earnings on Friday, July 24, 2026. The company will present results on a webcast beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET. Access instructions and second-quarter 2026 materials, including Verizon’s press release and financial tables, will be available at 7:00 a.m. ET on Verizon’s Investor Relations website, https://www.verizon.com/about/investors. This announcement was originally published",
